RoboRodentia2014
================

Code for Our RoboRodentia team for 2014

Necessary software components:
	-Omniwheel control
		-Move forward
		-Move side to side
		-Stop in certain places
			-Use of rotary Encoders
	-Ball moving system
		-Ramp with gate
		-
	-Infrared sensors 
		-Stop when front of robot reaches line
		-Stop when side of robot reaches line
		-Move side to side with front of robot aligned with black line
	-Reload LED
		-Turn on a green reloading LED when the side black lines are reached
		-Turn off the LED when we are done reloading (or after a set time)
	-Change of Behaviour at 2 minutes
		-Incase of orange ball
	
